message: Hello! Thank you for choosing Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I just wanted to say that I'm really pleased with the service I've received so far. Everyone has been so helpful!
That's wonderful to hear! We always strive to provide the best service to our customers. Before proceeding, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Of course, my name is Sarah Johnson.
Great, thank you Sarah. Could you also confirm your date of birth?
Perfect, thank you. And finally, could you confirm the first line of your address and postcode?
My address is 123 Oak Street, AB1 2CD.
Thank you for completing security, Sarah. How can I assist you further today?
I actually have a question about my policy. I recently had an accident and need to understand what's covered.
I'm sorry to hear about your accident, Sarah. Let me see how we can help. One possible resolution could be to review your policy details to determine the coverage. Would you like me to do that?
Yes, that would be great. Thank you so much for your help!
I've checked your policy, Sarah, and it looks like the damages from the accident are covered. Is there anything else you would like to know or need assistance with?
That's all sorted, thank you for your help, Chris. I really appreciate it.
You're welcome, Sarah! I'm glad that I was able to help. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
